        <abstract>
            <p>Sends photographs of himself and his late wife [Anna Sethe]. Describes death of his wife.</p>
            <p>Plans trip to the Alps.</p>
            <p>Thanks CD for biographical information about himself.</p>
            <p>Mentions Goethe as early evolutionist.</p>
            <p>Cites Kant as early supporter of epigenesis.</p> 
<p>Mentions criticism of CD’s theory by R. A. von Kölliker ["Über die Darwin’sche Schöpfungstheorie", <hi rend="italic">Z. Wiss. Zool.</hi> 14 (1864): 174–86].</p> 
        </abstract>
